{
  "stem": "8786.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So when my father passed away 26 years ago yesterday, I wrote to my brother, thank you, Almighty God, that He lended for us, for another nice couple of years.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because this was nothing but a gift, that he did survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because most of the-- most of people over 40-- even younger-- most of the young people didn't survive either.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But especially older ones, didn't have a chance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Wels-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from Wels, we-- I registered that I'm a Czechoslovak.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought I'm going to have a better chance to get home as soon as possible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and if I get home, what will wait for me at home, that was just a very, very hard secret, which nobody, nobody could guess.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody was-- as a matter of fact, I wrote a letter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wrote a letter from Wels to my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he got it-- to Tornal'a.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm just reminding myself that I did write a letter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he knew that I was-- that I survived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I took my little package, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I noticed that-- and I went to the train, to Prague.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But believe it or not, I was not strong enough to pick up my package on my shoulder.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I had to ask one of the-- one of the train men, he should-- [NON-ENGLISH], they call it-- he should help me up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't-- I, I forgot my, my, my Slovak language that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I told him [NON-ENGLISH], he should help me to-- I should be able to step up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was 17-- 16 years old when I couldn't-- I couldn't step-- I couldn't step up on the train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Over there, the steps are probably higher than what we have here.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
